Class KernelListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • kernel.KernelListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KernelListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StandardWorldModelViewerComponent

    public class KernelListenerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements KernelListener
    Abstract class for objects that want to implement a subset of the KernelListener interface. All default method implementations do nothing.
